						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">(very) little people running around in panic</div><br />This is in the latest build, along with a minor shout-out to Metal Gear series. And yes, they're very little, as in 4 pixels tall during gameplay and 8 pixels tall in the cut scenes.<br /><br />I tried asymmetric explosions like the ones in the Mega Man 4 (GB) intro; they made it a bit harder to see the hitboxes' center of mass.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle">qbradq wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I'm glad to hear your project is progressing Tepples! What are your plans for it? Will you give away the ROM when you are done or are you going to publish it on a cart?</div>
